msgid "12000:人を恋する気持ちは、妄想の存在でも抱けるものなのかな。[linebreak]それとも錯覚なのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:Could a delusion even fall in love? Or was I maybe just imagining things?[%p]"

msgid "12100:分からないけど、[%p]"
msgstr "12100:I couldn't tell.[%p]"

msgid "12200:僕は、[%p]"
msgstr "12200:I...[%p]"

msgid "12300:この気持ちに素直でありたい。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:I wanted to be honest about these feelings.[%p]"

msgid "12400:梨深は僕を友達として見ている。[linebreak]きっと異性として意識してくれてはいない。[linebreak]そもそも僕みたいなキモオタじゃ、梨深とは釣り合わない。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:Rimi saw me as a friend. Not as a potential boyfriend. And a creepy loser like me wasn't anywhere near worthy of her.[%p]"

msgid "12500:でも……たとえ片想いでも、自己満足でも、自分が妄想の存在だとしても、せめて、誰かのために……梨深のためになにかをして、消えていきたい。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:But... even if it was just one way, even if it was just for my own self-satisfaction, even if I was just a delusion... I wanted to do something to help someone, to help Rimi, before I disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "12600:キモオタが、恋をするのは、キモイ。[linebreak]妄想の存在が、恋をするのは、キモイ。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:When a creepy otaku falls in love, it's creepy. When a delusion falls in love, it's creepy.[%p]"

msgid "12700:だから、どうした？[%p]"
msgstr "12700:But so what?[%p]"

msgid "12800:キモくても、"
msgstr "12800:Even if it's creepy,"

msgid "12900:[linebreak]報われなくても、"
msgstr "12900:[linebreak]even if it's never going to happen..."

msgid "13000:[linebreak]僕は、[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[linebreak]I still...[%p]"

msgid "13100:キモくても、報われなくても、僕は、"
msgstr "13100:Even if it's creepy, even if it's never going to happen... I still..."

msgid "13200:この気持ちを、錯覚や妄想として片付けたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:I didn't want these feelings to be a delusion or my imagination.[%p]"

msgid "13300:この１ヶ月の想い出は、僕と、梨深、２人の周囲共通認識。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:Our memories of the past month were a shared awareness between me and Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "13400:他がすべてまやかしだったとしても。[linebreak]この想い出と。[linebreak]それを積み重ねて生まれた気持ちは。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:Even if everything else was a lie... These memories, and the feelings they created...[%p]"

msgid "13500:本物だ――[%p]"
msgstr "13500:were real.[%p]"

msgid "13600:[name]タクミ[line]「世界を救ってほしい」[%p]"
msgstr "13600:[name]タクミ[line]I want you to save the world.[%p]"

msgid "13700:『将軍』が、言う。[linebreak]僕は、首を振る。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:Shogun spoke. I shook my head.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「僕は勇者じゃない。人間でもない」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]I'm not a hero. I'm not even human.[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]拓巳[line]「そんな僕に、世界を救えとか……なにを考えてるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]拓巳[line]And you want me to save the world? What are you thinking?[%p]"

msgid "14000:[name]タクミ[line]「君には本当に悪いと思ってるけど、君にやってもらうしかないんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "14000:[name]タクミ[line]I really am sorry, but you're the only one who can.[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]拓巳[line]「自分に謝るなんて、バカみたいだ」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]拓巳[line]You sound like an idiot, apologizing to yourself.[%p]"

msgid "14200:僕は、本物の僕を、にらみつけた。[linebreak]本物の僕は、ニセモノの僕の視線を、受け止めた。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I glared at the real me. The real me stared back at the fake me.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]拓巳[line]「僕は、君が嫌いだ」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]拓巳[line]I hate you.[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]タクミ[line]「僕は、君が羨ましいよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]タクミ[line]I'm jealous of you.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]拓巳[line]「僕は世界のためになんか頑張らない」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]拓巳[line]I'm not going to do a thing to save the world.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]拓巳[line]「世界を救うとか、そんなことどうでもいい」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]拓巳[line]I don't care what happens to it.[%p]"

msgid "14700:自分が生まれた意味は、自分で決める。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:I'd decide for myself the reason I was born.[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]拓巳[line]「ただ……僕は、梨深を……助ける」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]拓巳[line]But... I will save Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]タクミ[line]「……ありがとう」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]タクミ[line]… Thank you.[%p]"

msgid "15000:周囲の音が、戻ってくる。[linebreak]混乱にますます拍車がかかっている。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:The sounds around me returned. The confusion around me had only increased.[%p]"

msgid "15100:もう、これは暴動だ。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:At this point, it was a riot.[%p]"

msgid "15200:僕の周囲は、血の匂いと、怒号と、悲鳴と、うめき声、そして……ハウリングしているかのような機械音。それらで溢れかえっている。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I was surrounded by the smell of blood, by screaming, by pained moans... and the noise of some kind of machine, like a microphone feeding back onto itself. It was everywhere.[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]拓巳[line]「ディソードを手に入れる方法を教えて」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]拓巳[line]Tell me how to get a Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "15400:[name]タクミ[line]「君は、すでにそれを知っているはずだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15400:[name]タクミ[line]You already know.[%p]"

msgid "15500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "15500:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "15600:視線を上げる。[linebreak]この景色の中に溶け込んでいる、剣の姿を探す。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I looked up. I tried to find the Di-Sword, blended in with the scenery.[%p]"

msgid "15700:石が飛び交い、[linebreak]催涙弾の煙が立ちのぼり、[linebreak]周囲の人が何度も身体をぶつけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:Flying rocks... Tear gas smoke... People colliding all around me.[%p]"

msgid "15800:その状況で、僕は意識を集中させて、かつてＯ－ＦＲＯＮＴの屋上から一瞬だけ見えたあの剣を、求める。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:I shut out all of it, and searched for the sword I'd seen for just an instant on the roof of O-FRONT.[%p]"

msgid "15900:見えているはず。[linebreak]どこかに、必ず、ある。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I should be able to see it. It should be there.[%p]"

msgid "16000:景色の一部。[linebreak]紛れ込んでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:Part of the scenery... Blended in...[%p]"

msgid "16100:捉えろ。[linebreak]ディソードは、いつも、そばにある。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Find it. The Di-Sword is always by your side.[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]拓巳[line]「……見つけた」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]拓巳[line]Found it.[%p]"

msgid "16300:１０７のすぐ右にあるビル。そこに縦に設置されたカラフルな看板。[linebreak]それが、剣の形に見えた。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:The building just to the right of the 107. There was a colorful vertical sign plastered to its side. It looked to me like the shape of a sword.[%p]"

msgid "16400:緊張。[linebreak]ゴクリと息を呑む。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:I gulped, nervously.[%p]"

msgid "16500:前にＯ－ＦＲＯＮＴの屋上から見たときも、剣の形を捉えることはできた。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:I'd been able to see its shape on top of the O-FRONT building, too.[%p]"

msgid "16600:でもあのときは、結局この手につかむことはできなかったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:But I hadn't been able to grab it.[%p]"

msgid "16700:[name]タクミ[line]「自分の意志を強く持つんだ。迷っちゃダメだからね」[%p]"
msgstr "16700:[name]タクミ[line]Clear your mind. Keep it steady and focused.[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]タクミ[line]「君にはもう、剣を手に入れる資格はじゅうぶんにある」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]タクミ[line]You've more than earned the right to own the sword.[%p]"

msgid "16900:その場に立ったまま、手を、伸ばす。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I reached out from where I stood.[%p]"

msgid "17000:大切な人を、助け出すために。[linebreak]その剣は、どうしても必要なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:If I was going to save the person I loved... I needed this sword.[%p]"

msgid "17100:どうしても――！[%p]"
msgstr "17100:I needed it![%p]"

msgid "17200:奥歯を噛みしめる。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:I bit down on my lower teeth.[%p]"

msgid "17300:前とは違う。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:This wasn't like last time.[%p]"

msgid "17400:心は、自分でも驚くぐらい穏やか。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I was surprised at how calm my heart was.[%p]"

msgid "17500:怯えはない。怯えてるわけにはいかない。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:There was no fear. I couldn't let myself be afraid.[%p]"

msgid "17600:でも冷静ってわけじゃなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:But I wasn't calm, either.[%p]"

msgid "17700:沸々と、煮えたぎっている感情がある。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:There was an emotion burning and boiling up inside me.[%p]"

msgid "17800:僕には、どうしても、やらなくちゃいけないことが、"
msgstr "17800:There was something I had to do,"

msgid "17900:ある――！[%p]"
msgstr "17900: no matter what![%p]"

msgid "18000:僕には、どうしても、やらなくちゃいけないことが、ある――！"
msgstr "18000:There was something I had to do, no matter what!"

msgid "18100:[name]タクミ[line]「つかむんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "18100:[name]タクミ[line]Grab it.[%p]"

msgid "18200:１０７までの距離はおよそ１００メートル。[linebreak]掌を、剣に重なって見えるようにして。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:I was about 100 meters from the 107. I moved my hand so that it seemed to overlap with the blade...[%p]"

msgid "18300:握りしめる。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:And clenched.[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]拓巳[line]「……！」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "18500:なにもないところを握ったはずなのに。[linebreak]手応えが、あった。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:My hand was reaching out into empty, open space, but I felt something.[%p]"

msgid "18600:それは、[linebreak]冷たくもなく、熱くもなく。[linebreak]硬くもなく、柔らかくもなく。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:It wasn't cold, or hot, or hard, or soft.[%p]"

msgid "18700:つかんだまま、ゆっくりと引き寄せた。[%p]"
msgstr "18700:I slowly pulled it toward me, holding it tight in my hand.[%p]"

msgid "18800:空間に浮かび上がる、波紋。[linebreak]その波紋の中から、ずるりと、せり出してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:Ripples appeared in the air. And out of the ripples, it came.[%p]"

msgid "18900:剣と呼ぶには、あまりに長く。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:Far too long to be called a sword...[%p]"

msgid "19000:今にも折れそうなほどの繊細さと。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:So delicate, it felt like it could snap at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "19100:夢幻なる気品に満ちて。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:Filled with an unearthly elegance,[%p]"

msgid "19200:絢爛さは露ほどもなく。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:but not a trace of ornamentation.[%p]"

msgid "19300:魂が吸い取られるかのような、清純なる悪意と。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:Pure malice that threatened to drain away your soul.[%p]"

msgid "19400:畏怖を感じさせるかのような流麗さを持ち合わせ。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:Beautiful curves that inspired awe and fear...[%p]"

msgid "19500:僕の高揚する心とリンクして、柄の部分に宿る禍々しい炎の意匠が揺らめく。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:The flames decorating its hilt flickered in time with the beating of my racing heart.[%p]"

msgid "19600:重さは欠片も感じない。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:It didn't feel heavy at all.[%p]"

msgid "19700:むしろ、手と完全に一体化したかのような。[linebreak]初めから、そこにあったかのような。[linebreak]僕の身体の一部であるかのような。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:In fact, it felt like it had become one with my hand. Like it had always been there, a part of my body.[%p]"

msgid "19800:剣を持っているという実感が湧かない。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:It didn't feel like I was really holding a sword at all.[%p]"

msgid "19900:これが……ディソード……！[%p]"
msgstr "19900:So, this... was a Di-Sword![%p]"

msgid "20000:両手で、きつく握りしめて。[linebreak]今の僕なら、これをリアルブートすることだってできるはず。[%p]"
msgstr "20000:I held it tight with both hands. Right now, I could real boot it, too.[%p]"

msgid "20100:周囲と共通の認識にすれば、この剣は、現実に姿を浮かび上がらせる。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:If I could make the people around me aware of it, too, this sword would become real.[%p]"

msgid "20200:やり方なんて、分からない。[linebreak]ただ、念じる。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:I didn't know how. So, I just focused.[%p]"

msgid "20300:現実になれと、心の中で叫ぶ。[linebreak]迷いは、もうない。[%p]"
msgstr "20300:Become real! I shouted in my mind. There was no more hesitation.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]拓巳[line]「ああああ――っ」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]拓巳[line]Aaah...![%p]"

msgid "20500:ディソードが、僕のその叫びに応えるように、淡く輝き始めた。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:The Di-Sword began to glow, as if in answer to my call.[%p]"

msgid "20600:柄の部分にある炎の意匠が、現実の炎となって剣を包み込む。熱さは感じない。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:The decorative flames on the hilt became real, engulfing the blade in fire. I didn't feel any heat.[%p]"

msgid "20700:その炎はやがて、剣全体に吸い込まれていき――[%p]"
msgstr "20700:The flames were soon absorbed by the whole blade...[%p]"

msgid "20800:激しい衝撃とともに、ディソードは紅い光を帯びた。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:And with a violent shockwave, the Di-Sword glowed red.[%p]"

msgid "20900:周りにいた一部の人たちが、僕の剣を目にして驚き、呆然としている。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:Some of the people around me saw the weapon and were watching in shock.[%p]"

msgid "21000:でも一部だけだ。[linebreak]他の人たちは、殴り合い、罵り合うことに夢中。[linebreak]暴動は収まりそうにない。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:But only a few. The others were still fighting and cursing one another. The riot showed no signs of stopping.[%p]"

msgid "21100:[name]タクミ[line]「この暴動を引き起こしているポーターたちを探すんだ。彼らの持つ機械を破壊すれば、バイオリズムの高騰も収まる」[%p]"
msgstr "21100:[name]タクミ[line]Look for the Porters who are causing the riot. If you can destroy the devices they hold, the crowd's biorhythms will return to normal.[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]拓巳[line]「ポーター？」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]拓巳[line]Porters?[%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]タクミ[line]「ノアⅡの端末としての存在」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]タクミ[line]Terminals of Noah II.[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]タクミ[line]「君は、すでにそのヒントを“見てきた”はずだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]タクミ[line]You've already seen the hint you need.[%p]"

msgid "21500:[name]タクミ[line]「君の頭の中に、それは記憶として刻まれている」[%p]"
msgstr "21500:[name]タクミ[line]The memories exist within your mind.[%p]"

msgid "21600:呼び覚ます。[linebreak]僕が“見てきた”ものを。[%p]"
msgstr "21600:I awakened it, the thing I'd seen...[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]あやせ[line]「Fly and cross Fly and cross 約束は今――」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]あやせ[line]Fly and cross, fly and cross, the promise is now...[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]梢[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "21900:[name]判[line]「ようやくシッポを出したんだ。[linebreak]そいつをつかんで離さねえようにしないとな……」[%p]"
msgstr "21900:[name]判[line]We've finally got a lead. Time to make sure it doesn't go to waste.[%p]"

msgid "22000:[name]優愛[line]「辛いんですね……」[%p]"
msgstr "22000:[name]優愛[line]It's painful, isn't it?[%p]"

msgid "22100:[name]判[line]「有限会社シンコー……聞いたことあるかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "22100:[name]判[line]Thinko, LLC. You heard of them?[%p]"

msgid "22200:[name]七海[line]「返して……ナナのバングル、返して……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "22200:[name]七海[line]Give it back... Give back my bangle.[%p]"

msgid "22300:[name]清掃員Ａ[line]「地点Ｌ２－８、０．６２メガＧＥ。ハイスコアです」[%p]"
msgstr "22300:[name]清掃員Ａ[line]Point L2-8,0. 62 mega-GE. A new high score.[%p]"

msgid "22400:[name]判[line]「どんな手品だ、こりゃ……」[%p]"
msgstr "22400:[name]判[line]What kind of magic trick is this?[%p]"

msgid "22500:[name]セナ[line]「ＮＯＺＯＭＩ……」[%p]"
msgstr "22500:[name]セナ[line]NOZOMI...[%p]"

msgid "22600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「我が社では『ポーター』と呼んでいます」[%p]"
msgstr "22600:[name]野呂瀬[line]We call them Porters.[%p]"

msgid "22700:[name]野呂瀬[line]「言い換えれば、マインドコントロールのための部隊、といったところでしょうか」[%p]"
msgstr "22700:[name]野呂瀬[line]You might call them our mind control squad.[%p]"

msgid "22800:僕が、ずっと、無意識のうちに見てきたもの。[linebreak]無意識のうちに、思考盗撮していたもの。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:The things I'd seen unconsciously... The things I'd unconsciously read with my mind...[%p]"

msgid "22900:[name]拓巳[line]「僕は盗撮野郎ってことか。お似合いだね」[%p]"
msgstr "22900:[name]拓巳[line]So, I'm the one who's been spying on people's minds. I guess that's appropriate.[%p]"

msgid "23000:自嘲気味に笑う僕に、『将軍』が冷静に指示してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "23000:I let out a small, self-deprecating chuckle as Shogun calmly gave me my next directions.[%p]"

msgid "23100:[name]タクミ[line]「チャネルを開放して、ポーターたちの心を読むんだ。“こずぴぃ”のようにね」[%p]"
msgstr "23100:[name]タクミ[line]Unlock the channels. Read the Porters' minds, like Kozupii does.[%p]"

msgid "23200:[name]タクミ[line]「彼らはこのスクランブル交差点の、どこかにいる。居場所を探り当てて」[%p]"
msgstr "23200:[name]タクミ[line]They're somewhere here in Scramble Crossing. Find them.[%p]"

msgid "23300:チャネルを開放する。[%p]"
msgstr "23300:Unlock the channels...[%p]"

msgid "23400:どうやればいいか、なんて考えるまでもなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "23400:I didn't even have to think about how I'd do it.[%p]"

msgid "23500:意識しなくても、感覚で僕はそれを実行していた。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:I'd already done it before I could even think about it.[%p]"

msgid "23600:直後、この場にいるたくさんの人たちの心が。[linebreak]負の感情が。[%p]"
msgstr "23600:And when I did, the minds of all these people, their negative emotions,[%p]"

msgid "23700:見えるようになって。[linebreak]一気に僕に流れ込んできた。[%p]"
msgstr "23700:all became visible to me. It all came flooding in at once.[%p]"

msgid "23800:[name]拓巳[line]「――――っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "23800:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "23900:悪意。憎悪。嫉妬。淫欲。卑屈。臆病。軽薄。汚濁。狡猾。卑猥。醜悪。下劣。情欲。狂気。殺意。[%p]"
msgstr "23900:Malice. Hatred. Jealousy. Lust. Subservience. Cowardice. Frivolity. Filth. Cunning. Indecency. Ugliness. Vulgarity. Greed. Madness. Murder.[%p]"

msgid "24000:言葉を通すよりも、よりダイレクトで、より残虐で、よりおぞましい、人が他人に隠している、醜い感情の発露。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:The hidden ugliness of all these people was revealed to me in a way more direct, more cruel, more terrible than words.[%p]"

msgid "24100:人の抱く、あらゆる負の感情が、イメージの奔流となって、僕の心を呑み込み、砕き、犯してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "24100:All the negative emotions mankind could possess came at me in a torrent of images, enveloping my mind, shattering and violating it.[%p]"

msgid "24200:蔑むような視線を浴び、"
msgstr "24200:They looked at me with disgust."

msgid "24300:[linebreak]侮蔑の言葉で罵られ、"
msgstr "24300:[linebreak]Hurt me with their words."

msgid "24400:[linebreak]唾を吐きかけられ、[%p]"
msgstr "24400:[linebreak]Spat on me.[%p]"

msgid "24500:蔑むような視線を浴び、侮蔑の言葉で罵られ、唾を吐きかけられ、"
msgstr "24500:They looked at me with disgust. Hurt me with their words. Spat on me."

msgid "24600:爪をはがされ、"
msgstr "24600:My nails were torn off."

msgid "24700:[linebreak]頬を拳で何度も殴られ、"
msgstr "24700:[linebreak]I was punched again and again in the face."

msgid "24800:[linebreak]尻を蹴られ、[%p]"
msgstr "24800:[linebreak]Kicked from behind.[%p]"

msgid "24900:爪をはがされ、頬を拳で何度も殴られ、尻を蹴られ、"
msgstr "24900:My nails were torn off. I was punched again and again in the face. Kicked from behind."

msgid "25000:髪の毛をむしり取られ、"
msgstr "25000:My hair was ripped out."

msgid "25100:[linebreak]鼻を噛み千切られ、"
msgstr "25100:[linebreak]My nose was bitten off."

msgid "25200:[linebreak]目玉をえぐり出され、[%p]"
msgstr "25200:[linebreak]My eyeballs were pulled from their sockets.[%p]"

msgid "25300:髪の毛をむしり取られ、鼻を噛み千切られ、目玉をえぐり出され、"
msgstr "25300:My hair was ripped out. My nose was bitten off. My eyeballs were pulled from their sockets."

msgid "25400:舌を引っ張り出され、"
msgstr "25400:My tongue was yanked from my mouth."

msgid "25500:[linebreak]血を吸い取られ、"
msgstr "25500:[linebreak]My blood was drained."

msgid "25600:[linebreak]熱湯を浴びて火傷させられ、[%p]"
msgstr "25600:[linebreak]I was burned by hot water.[%p]"

msgid "25700:舌を引っ張り出され、血を吸い取られ、熱湯を浴びて火傷させられ、"
msgstr "25700:My tongue was yanked from my mouth. My blood was drained. I was burned by hot water."

msgid "25800:肛門を犯され、"
msgstr "25800:My anus was raped."

msgid "25900:[linebreak]性器を叩き潰され、"
msgstr "25900:[linebreak]My genitals were smashed."

msgid "26000:[linebreak]全身の皮を剥がされ、[%p]"
msgstr "26000:[linebreak]My skin was torn off.[%p]"

msgid "26100:肛門を犯され、性器を叩き潰され、全身の皮を剥がされ、"
msgstr "26100:My anus was raped. My genitals were smashed. My skin was torn off."

msgid "26200:腕を斬られ、"
msgstr "26200:My arms were cut off."

msgid "26300:[linebreak]あらゆる箇所の骨を折られ、"
msgstr "26300:[linebreak]All my bones broken."

msgid "26400:[linebreak]鈍器で殴られ、[%p]"
msgstr "26400:[linebreak]I was struck with blunt weapons.[%p]"

msgid "26500:腕を斬られ、あらゆる箇所の骨を折られ、鈍器で殴られ、"
msgstr "26500:My arms were cut off. All my bones broken. I was struck with blunt weapons."

msgid "26600:刃物で刺され、"
msgstr "26600:Stabbed with sharp ones."

msgid "26700:[linebreak]内臓をえぐり取られ、"
msgstr "26700:[linebreak]My organs were torn out."

msgid "26800:[linebreak]首をきつく絞められ、[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[linebreak]I was strangled.[%p]"

msgid "26900:刃物で刺され、内臓をえぐり取られ、首をきつく絞められ、"
msgstr "26900:Stabbed with sharp ones. My organs were torn out. I was strangled."

msgid "27000:巨大な獣に肉を食われ、"
msgstr "27000:Eaten by huge beasts."

msgid "27100:[linebreak]高所から突き落とされ、"
msgstr "27100:[linebreak]Pushed off high places."

msgid "27200:[linebreak]水の中で窒息させられ、[%p]"
msgstr "27200:[linebreak]Drowned in the water.[%p]"

msgid "27300:巨大な獣に肉を食われ、高所から突き落とされ、水の中で窒息させられ、"
msgstr "27300:Eaten by huge beasts. Pushed off high places. Drowned in the water."

msgid "27400:炎で全身を焼かれ――[%p]"
msgstr "27400:Burnt in the flames.[%p]"

msgid "27500:同調してしまったら、僕の心が壊れる。気が狂いそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:If I synchronized with them all, my mind would shatter. I felt like I was going crazy.[%p]"

msgid "27600:歯を食いしばって、自分の意識を必死で保つ。[%p]"
msgstr "27600:I bit my teeth and tried as hard as I could to focus.[%p]"

msgid "27700:こずぴぃはこんな状態でずっと生きてきたって言うの？[%p]"
msgstr "27700:Had Kozupii lived her whole life like this?[%p]"

msgid "27800:[name]タクミ[line]「見るべき妄想をコントロールするんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "27800:[name]タクミ[line]Control the delusions so that you see what you need to see.[%p]"

msgid "27900:[name]タクミ[line]「すべてを受信しちゃダメだ。標的を絞り込んで」[%p]"
msgstr "27900:[name]タクミ[line]Don't try to take them all in. Narrow your target.[%p]"

msgid "28000:[name]タクミ[line]「“音”を頼りにするんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "28000:[name]タクミ[line]Rely on the sound.[%p]"

msgid "28100:音――[%p]"
msgstr "28100:Sound...[%p]"

msgid "28200:押し寄せる負の妄想に耐えながら、必死で耳を澄ます。[%p]"
msgstr "28200:I listened as hard as I could, struggling to fight off the waves of delusions.[%p]"

msgid "28300:聞こえてくるのは、声ばかり。[linebreak]それらを遮断し。[linebreak]音を探す。[%p]"
msgstr "28300:All I could hear were voices. I shut them out, and searched for the sound.[%p]"

msgid "28400:聞こえてくる、機械音。[linebreak]“僕を殺してくれる音”って星来たんが言っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "28400:I heard it, a mechanical sound. The sound Seira-tan had said would kill me.[%p]"

msgid "28500:思考盗撮した記憶の中にも、この音がある。[linebreak]セナがこの音を発するポーターのリュックを、ディソードで破壊していた。[%p]"
msgstr "28500:I'd heard it in the memories of others, too. Sena had used her Di-Sword to destroy the Porter's backpack that had been emitting this sound.[%p]"

msgid "28600:その音に意識を向ければ――[%p]"
msgstr "28600:If I focused on it...[%p]"

msgid "28700:聞こえてくる妄想は、[%p]"
msgstr "28700:I could hear a very specific delusion.[%p]"

msgid "28800:[name]みんな[line]「神光の救いあれ。神光の救いあれ……」[%p]"
msgstr "28800:[name]みんな[line]May the Divine Light save us... May the Divine Light save us...[%p]"

msgid "28900:声は、複数あった。[linebreak]この場にいるポーターは、ひとりじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "28900:There were multiple voices. There was more than just one Porter here, it seemed.[%p]"

msgid "29000:[name]タクミ[line]「３人いるみたいだね」[%p]"
msgstr "29000:[name]タクミ[line]Three of them.[%p]"

msgid "29100:息を殺して、僕は一歩を踏み出す。[%p]"
msgstr "29100:I held my breath and took a step forward.[%p]"

msgid "29200:混沌とした人の群れ。秩序の欠片もなく、それぞれが好き勝手に歩き回り、殴り合っている、このスクランブル交差点。まっすぐ進むことは困難。[%p]"
msgstr "29200:The crowd was chaotic. Everyone in Scramble Crossing was moving around, fighting, without the slightest regard for any other human being. It was hard to walk straight.[%p]"

msgid "29300:僕は標的の方向にいる人々の妄想をハックした。[%p]"
msgstr "29300:I hacked into the delusions of the people in the direction I was going.[%p]"

msgid "29400:僕の視界の先にいた人たちが、少しずつ立つ場所をずらしていく。[linebreak]そこに、一筋の道ができた。[%p]"
msgstr "29400:The people in front of me began to part. They made a path before me.[%p]"

msgid "29500:５０メートルほど先に、ひとりの男。[linebreak]僕とその男との間にあるあらゆる障害物が、今、除かれた。[%p]"
msgstr "29500:Fifty meters away, I saw a single man. There was nothing standing between us now.[%p]"

msgid "29600:目が合う。[%p]"
msgstr "29600:Our eyes met.[%p]"

msgid "29700:小太りで、スーツ姿で、リュックを背負っている。[%p]"
msgstr "29700:He was pudgy, wearing a suit, and carrying a backpack.[%p]"

msgid "29800:[name]拓巳[line]「１人目……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "29800:[name]拓巳[line]Number one...[%p]"

msgid "29900:走る。[%p]"
msgstr "29900:I ran.[%p]"

msgid "30000:この人ごみの中を。[%p]"
msgstr "30000:I ran through the crowd...[%p]"

msgid "30100:誰にもぶつかることなく。[%p]"
msgstr "30100:without running into anyone.[%p]"

msgid "30200:まっすぐに。[%p]"
msgstr "30200:Straight ahead,[%p]"

msgid "30300:最短距離で。[%p]"
msgstr "30300:via the fastest possible route,[%p]"

msgid "30400:ディソードを引きずりながら。[%p]"
msgstr "30400:trailing the Di-Sword behind me.[%p]"

msgid "30500:[name]ポーターＢ[line]「な、なんで――」[%p]"
msgstr "30500:[name]ポーターＢ[line]H-How?[%p]"

msgid "30600:僕に気付いたポーターの男は、慌てた様子で背を向け、逃げ出そうとする。[linebreak]でも僕はそれを許さない。[%p]"
msgstr "30600:When the Porter saw me, he turned tail and tried to run. But I wouldn't let him.[%p]"

msgid "30700:セナと同じように。[linebreak]僕の背丈よりも長いディソードを、横凪ぎに払う。[%p]"
msgstr "30700:Just like Sena had done, I swung the huge Di-Sword, even taller than I was, in a horizontal arc.[%p]"

msgid "30800:相変わらず、重さを感じない。[linebreak]自分の手の一部のように操れる。[%p]"
msgstr "30800:It still seemed to weigh nothing. I could control it like it was a part of my body.[%p]"

msgid "30900:ディソードの先端が、リュックを抉った。[linebreak]高温で溶かされたように。[linebreak]リュックは中身ごと蒸発した。[%p]"
msgstr "30900:Its tip sliced into the backpack. The backpack and its contents were vaporized, as if they'd been melted by something impossibly hot.[%p]"

msgid "31000:男はその場にへたり込み、頭を抱えて震えている。[%p]"
msgstr "31000:The man dropped to his knees, holding his hands over his head to protect himself.[%p]"

msgid "31100:そいつには目もくれず、２人目へ。[%p]"
msgstr "31100:I ignored him and headed for the second one...[%p]"

msgid "31200:Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴの下。[%p]"
msgstr "31200:directly beneath O-FRONT.[%p]"

msgid "31300:再びそこに至る障害物が消えていく。[linebreak]道が築かれていく。[%p]"
msgstr "31300:Once again, the obstacles between us disappeared. A path formed.[%p]"

msgid "31400:その先に立つ男。[linebreak]痩せぎすで、チェックのシャツにジーパンという格好。[%p]"
msgstr "31400:A man was standing there. He was rail-thin, and wearing jeans and a checkered shirt.[%p]"

msgid "31500:長髪で、病的に肌が白い。[linebreak]バッグを大事そうに胸に抱えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "31500:His hair was long and his skin was sickly pale. He was holding his bag carefully, like it contained some dear treasure.[%p]"

msgid "31600:そいつは僕に気付くなり、人ごみの中に紛れ込もうとした。[linebreak]それよりも先に、"
msgstr "31600:He noticed me and immediately tried to hide within the crowd. But before he could,"

msgid "31700:ディソードを、投擲する。[%p]"
msgstr "31700: I threw the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "31800:そいつは僕に気付くなり、人ごみの中に紛れ込もうとした。[linebreak]それよりも先に、ディソードを、投擲する。"
msgstr "31800:He noticed me and immediately tried to hide within the crowd. But before he could, I threw the Di-Sword."

msgid "31900:――飛べ。[%p]"
msgstr "31900:—Fly.[%p]"

msgid "32000:妄想した。[%p]"
msgstr "32000:I envisioned the scene in my delusion.[%p]"

msgid "32100:それは物理法則を無視し、[linebreak]地面と並行に、[linebreak]加速しながら飛翔する。[%p]"
msgstr "32100:It ignored all laws of physics, flying parallel to the ground and accelerating as it went.[%p]"

msgid "32200:微妙に軌道を修正し、[linebreak]正確無比に、ポーター男のバッグを貫く。[%p]"
msgstr "32200:It subtly altered its course as it flew, and rammed right through the porter's backpack.[%p]"

msgid "32300:かすかな閃光を発して。[linebreak]男はその場に倒れた。[%p]"
msgstr "32300:There was a small burst of light, and the man toppled to the ground.[%p]"

msgid "32400:あと、ひとり――[%p]"
msgstr "32400:One left.[%p]"

msgid "32500:倒れた男のところへ駆け寄り、ディソードを回収。[linebreak]３人目は、ハチ公の前。[%p]"
msgstr "32500:I ran over to the fallen man and recovered my Di-Sword. The third was in front of the Hachiko statue.[%p]"

msgid "32600:そのポーターとは、[linebreak]僕は、何度か会ったことがある。[%p]"
msgstr "32600:I knew this one. I'd encountered them a few times before.[%p]"

msgid "32700:いや、もっと正確に言うなら、[%p]"
msgstr "32700:Actually, in fact...[%p]"

msgid "32800:ほぼ毎日のように、話をしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "32800:I'd talked to her almost every day.[%p]"

msgid "32900:人の波が分かれて。[linebreak]三度、一直線に道が現れる。[%p]"
msgstr "32900:The crowd parted, and once again a path was formed.[%p]"

msgid "33000:その道の先に。[linebreak]とても目立つ、白い服を着た女。[%p]"
msgstr "33000:At the end of it, I saw a woman who looked very out of place. She was in a white nurse's outfit.[%p]"

msgid "33100:[name]拓巳[line]「あなたが、３人目です」[%p]"
msgstr "33100:[name]拓巳[line]So, you're the third Porter.[%p]"

msgid "33200:[name]拓巳[line]「葉月さん……いや……グリム」[%p]"
msgstr "33200:[name]拓巳[line]Hazuki... No, Grimm.[%p]"

msgid "33300:病院で、優しい笑みを浮かべていた看護師。[%p]"
msgstr "33300:The nurse who'd smiled so kindly at me at the hospital.[%p]"

msgid "33400:今、彼女は刺すような眼差しで僕をにらんでいる。[linebreak]手には、大きめのハンドバッグ。[linebreak]おそらくあの中に、ノアⅡの端末がある。[%p]"
msgstr "33400:Now she was glaring at me, daggers in her eyes. There was a large handbag in her hands. It was probably a Noah II terminal.[%p]"

msgid "33500:[name]タクミ[line]「真実を、暴くんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "33500:[name]タクミ[line]Reveal the truth.[%p]"

msgid "33600:[name]タクミ[line]「彼女がしてきたことを、この場にいる人たちに提示すれば――」[%p]"
msgstr "33600:[name]タクミ[line]If you show the people here what she's done...[%p]"

msgid "33700:[name]タクミ[line]「この熱病のような混乱は収まる」[%p]"
msgstr "33700:[name]タクミ[line]The chaos will end.[%p]"

msgid "33800:してきたこと？[%p]"
msgstr "33800:What she's done?[%p]"

msgid "33900:[name]タクミ[line]「彼女が“グリム”なら、これまでの不自然な言動に、君は気付いているはず」[%p]"
msgstr "33900:[name]タクミ[line]If she's “Grimm,” then you should have noticed some things that didn't make sense.[%p]"

msgid "34000:[name]タクミ[line]「僕が最初に君に接触したときのことを、思い出して」[%p]"
msgstr "34000:[name]タクミ[line]Remembered the first time we spoke.[%p]"

msgid "34100:[name]タクミ[line]「僕は君に、『張り付け』事件の予言をした。君への警鐘だった」[%p]"
msgstr "34100:[name]タクミ[line]I told you about the Crucified murder. It was a warning to you.[%p]"

msgid "34200:[name]タクミ[line]「でも、僕よりも、先に――」[%p]"
msgstr "34200:[name]タクミ[line]But before I did...[%p]"

msgid "34300:[name]タクミ[line]「『張り付け』を予言した人間が、いる」[%p]"
msgstr "34300:[name]タクミ[line]Someone else had told you about it, too.[%p]"

msgid "34400:[name]拓巳[line]「……！」[%p]"
msgstr "34400:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "34500:思い出す。[linebreak]あのときのチャットでのやり取りを。[%p]"
msgstr "34500:I remembered. I remembered the chat log from that night.[%p]"

msgid "34600:『将軍』が僕に語りかけてくる直前。[linebreak]グリムは退室した。[linebreak]ひとつのネタ画像を添付して。[%p]"
msgstr "34600:Just before Shogun had spoken to me... Grimm had left the room, along with a joke image he'd drawn.[%p]"

msgid "34700:葉月さんがカルテにも落書きしていた、あの絵。[linebreak]稚拙な絵だけど、それが表しているのは――[linebreak]『張り付け』だ。[%p]"
msgstr "34700:It was the one that Hazuki had been drawing on the medical charts. It was a very poorly-drawn picture, but what it showed was... The Crucified murder.[%p]"

msgid "34800:それにグリムは、ニュージェネ事件について[linebreak]僕に最初に説明したとき、こう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "34800:And then there was what Grimm had said about the NewGen murders, too.[%p]"

msgid "34900:“全部おまいん家の近所だぞｗ”[%p]"
msgstr "34900:It's all happening right near your house, lol[%p]"

msgid "35000:僕が渋谷に住んでいることは、一言も教えていなかったのに。[%p]"
msgstr "35000:I'd never told him I lived in Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "35100:つい数時間前のチャットでも、グリムは僕が西條拓巳だと把握しているかのような言葉を漏らした。[%p]"
msgstr "35100:And even just a few hours ago, Grimm had said something that showed he knew I was Takumi Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "35200:“おまいは有名人だから祭り会場で注目の的だお”[%p]"
msgstr "35200:You're famous. They'll all be excited to see you.[%p]"

msgid "35300:二度目に僕が病院に行ったとき。[linebreak]葉月さんは、こう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "35300:And then the second time I'd gone to the hospital... Hazuki had said this:[%p]"

msgid "35400:[name]葉月[line]「高科先生は、もういません……」[%p]"
msgstr "35400:[name]葉月[line]Dr. Takashina is gone.[%p]"

msgid "35500:その１週間後、高科先生は遺体となって発見された。[%p]"
msgstr "35500:A week later, Dr. Takashina was found dead.[%p]"

msgid "35600:ゴクリと、息を呑む。[%p]"
msgstr "35600:I gulped.[%p]"

msgid "35700:[name]拓巳[line]「あの人が……」[%p]"
msgstr "35700:[name]拓巳[line]So, she's...[%p]"

msgid "35800:[name]拓巳[line]「真犯人……？」[%p]"
msgstr "35800:[name]拓巳[line]The real killer?[%p]"

msgid "35900:“見れば”分かることだ。[linebreak]あの人の、心を――[%p]"
msgstr "35900:I could find out if I looked. If I looked into her mind...[%p]"

